This directory contains a beta release of the proposed device-mapper 
for the linux kernel.

For more information about the device mapper read the INTRO file.
Installation instructions are in INSTALL.

Tarballs are available from ftp://ftp.sistina.com/pub/LVM2/device-mapper/

To access the CVS tree use:
  cvs -d :pserver:cvs@tech.sistina.com:/data/cvs login
  CVS password: cvs1
  cvs -d :pserver:cvs@tech.sistina.com:/data/cvs checkout device-mapper

Mailing list for discussion/bug reports etc.
  lvm-devel@sistina.com
  Subscribe from http://lists.sistina.com/mailman/listinfo/lvm-devel

